DATA VISUALIZATION D3JS 

Advanced Task EXERCISE 2


This task consists on creating a Line Chart, add dots and interaction. Whenever you click on the dots display information
We start with the source code in lemoncode repository

1. Add dots to every register in TotalSales.
2. Add a title to the graphic.
3. Display text message.
4. Show the message with mouse click
5. Hide the message with mouse off

